      "text": "Un Jahseps nofatize ta\nPirmdsinta Wahrdnu Manassus/\njo (fazzija wiꞥſch:) Deews fr̄\nman lizzis aismirst/wiffu mannũ\nGruhtunu/ un wiffu manna\nTehwa Naminu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 52,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un ta ohtra Wahrdnu no-\nfauze wiꞥſch Eewrãim/ jo (faz-\nzija wiꞥſch:) Deews irr mannũ\nlizzis augt mannã Behdu Sem-\nme.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 53,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad beidsaḥs tee feptin\nbaggati Gaddi/ kas Egiptes-\nSemmẽ bija bijufcht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 54,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tee feptin Badda-\nGaddi fahze nahkt/ itt kã Jah-\nseps bij fazzijis/ un tur bija\nBads wits apkahrt fahrtim/bet\npa wiffu Egiptes-Semmi bija\nMaise.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 55,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kad nu wiffa Egiptes-\nSemme arri Baddu zeete/ tad\nbrehze Warãũs Landis pehz Mai-\nses: Bet Waraiis fazzija us wif-\nfeem Egiptexeem: Eita pee Jah-\nsepa/ fo tas jums fazzih̃s/ to\ndarrajt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 56,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kad nu Bads pa wiffu to\nSemmi bija/ tad atwehre Jah-\nseps wiffas Klehtis/un pahr dewe\nteem Egiptexeem/ jo tas Bads\nbija jo Deenas jo leelaks Egip-\ntes-Semmẽ.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 57,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiffas zittas Semmes\nTeefas nahze uhs Egiptes-Sem-\nmi pee Jahsepa pirkt/ jo tas\nBads bija leels wiffã Sem-\nmẽ.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ad nu Jehkabs t\nka Labbiba E\nSemmẽ bija/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch fazzija:\nes eſmu dsirdejis Labbibu\nEgiptes-Semmẽ/no-eita\nren/ un piczeet mums no\nnes/ ka mehs dsihwōjam\nmirſtam.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad nogahje definite\nsepa Brahti/ Labbibu no\ntes-Semmes pirkt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet Benjaminu/ J\nBrahti/ ne fuhtija Jehk-\nwinnã Brahteem/ jo tas fo\nka to jafchu ne fahda Lif\naisnemun.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tã nahze Israëla L\nLabbibu pirkt starp teim/ ka\ngahje/ jo Bads bija arr\nRandaña Semmẽ.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Jahseps bija p\nSemmi Walditajs/ un pah\nwiffeem tahs Semmes Lau\nun Jahsepa Brahti nahze\npaklannijahs preeksch wiṅg\nWaigu pee Semmes.\n"
    }
